a (web) render for https://sketchpad.keycurriculum.com/

cargo run ./path/to/your.gsp
cargo run ./path/to/one.gsp ./path/to/two.gsp

will generate:
- `./path/to/your.html`
- `./path/to/one.html`
- `./path/to/two.html`

architecture:
- `gsp` parsing stays separate from export.
- `runtime` builds a normalized scene plus interaction/runtime metadata.
- `export/html` turns that scene into a self-contained single HTML file.
- `pipeline` is the product boundary: `.gsp -> standalone html`.
